{"slug":"sirkuler-24-0734eng","reference":"Sirkuler_24_0734ENG","gazette":"Official Gazette No. 32673, dated 25 September 2024","title":"Changes have been made to the surveillance application on phone parts","date":"28 Eylül 2024","bodyHtml":"<p>Changes have been made to the surveillance practice regarding the components and parts of telephone devices.</p><p>The $100/unit surveillance&nbsp; for cards with at least one component (including motherboards) for telephone devices will now only be applied for motherboards. For other cards, the surveillance value will be $5/unit.<br></p><p>The change came into effect as of 25th of September.<br></p><p>The surveillance table of the Communiqué No. 2024/3, which regulates the surveillance practice regarding the components of telephone devices, is below.</p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"571\" style=\"caption-side: bottom; width: 427.9pt; border: none; outline: 0px !important;\"><tbody style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; outline: 0px !important;\"><tr style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; outline: 0px !important;\"><td width=\"3%\" rowspan=\"5\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-top: none; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: none; border-left: none; width: 15.9625px; border-image: initial; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; padding: 0.75pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><p class=\"3-NormalYaz\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: 0cm; margin-bottom: 1rem; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; line-height: 12pt; outline: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: 0px !important;\"></p></td><td width=\"15%\" style=\"border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: none; width: 88.875px; border-image